---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import PageHero from '../components/PageHero.astro';
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';
---
<Base
  title="About Academia Europa"
  description="A European professional education institution operated by Solex Education Unipessoal LDA, Portugal. Structured postgraduate learning pathways across specialised fields."
>
  <PageHero
    eyebrow="About"
    title="A European Institution for Postgraduate Professional Education."
    lede="Academia Europa develops structured professional learning for experienced practitioners who seek depth, progression, and lasting authority in their field."
  />

  <Section eyebrow="What Academia Europa Is" title="An institution, not a marketplace.">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Academia Europa is a European professional education institution operated by <strong class="text-navy-deep font-medium">Solex Education Unipessoal LDA</strong>, Portugal. It develops structured postgraduate professional learning pathways for experienced practitioners who seek depth, progression, and lasting professional authority.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Why It Exists" title="Continuing education, reimagined as progression." tone="ivory">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Across the professions, continuing education has become an inventory of isolated hours. It does not produce progression, and it rarely produces mastery. Academia Europa was founded to change this: to build a deliberate, long-term educational framework in which experienced professionals progress with clarity from competence to authority.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Identity" title="A European institution with an international outlook.">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Rooted in Portugal and shaped by European academic values, Academia Europa serves a global community of practitioners. Programmes are designed to travel across countries, languages, and professional traditions, while preserving the discipline of European postgraduate education.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Educational Scope" title="What Academia Europa provides, and where its boundary lies." tone="ivory">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Academia Europa provides structured postgraduate professional education and certificate programmes. It does not present itself as a university or state degree-awarding institution. Any external recognition, professional approval, or credit allocation is stated clearly where formally granted.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Our First Academy" title="Beginning with Veterinary Academy International.">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Veterinary Academy International is the first specialised academy of Academia Europa, dedicated to postgraduate veterinary education. Programme detail, faculty information, and the academy's educational directions are available on the dedicated VAI platform.</p>
      <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="/academies/vai" class="btn">Discover VAI</a>
        <a href="https://vai.vet" rel="noopener" class="btn">Visit VAI</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Long-Term Multi-Disciplinary Vision" title="Designed to extend across specialised fields." tone="ivory">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Academia Europa is being developed as a multi-disciplinary platform. Future academies are designed to support additional professional fields, including medicine, dentistry, pharmacy, law, artificial intelligence and digital transformation, technology, business, and leadership.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Leadership" title="Established under experienced leadership.">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Academia Europa was established under the leadership of Dr. Soheyl Simaei, a clinician, entrepreneur, and education founder with more than two decades of clinical and professional leadership experience. The institution is being developed as a multi-disciplinary platform for structured postgraduate professional education.</p>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <a href="/about/leadership" class="inline-block text-sm tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-navy hover:text-champagne">Read the leadership note →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section eyebrow="Legal Operator" tone="ivory">
    <div class="prose-editorial max-w-3xl">
      <p>Academia Europa is operated by <strong class="text-navy-deep font-medium">Solex Education Unipessoal LDA</strong>, registered in Portugal.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Base>
